{
  "stem": "24409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I expected the war to start any hour, not any day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the few days before, the pact between Ribbentrop and Stalin had been announced.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was clear that Hitler had now free hands in the East, so that he can attack in the West.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I figured-- I asked myself, what will happen here?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What will happen to our transport?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing that was clear to me was that Europe will be cut in two parts, along the axis-- Germany and Italy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was on the wrong side, here, because I could smuggle people from there, but I couldn't get them into Greece if it was under German control.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the Germans had, among themselves, quite some debate about whether they should favor this illegal transportation or not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, a few days before-- maybe two days before the 1st of September-- I went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought, I have to get to the train station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody will want to get to the train station, from the hotel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to the rescue squad and spoke, there, to the manager or officer, whoever it was, and told him that I wanted-- I make a substantial contribution for his rescue squad, but I will need him, when the war starts, [INAUDIBLE], he should be ready to wait for my call, and then he has to come and pick me up.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I heard-- in the morning, when I woke up, I heard that Germany had invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to the phone first, and called the rescue squad that they should call for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, I went down to pay, but there was a long line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to get home.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
